c, tam thập vận - 秋日荊南送石首薛明府辭滿告別奉寄薛尚書頌德敘懷斐然之作三十韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BB%AB-khanh-nh%E1%BB%8B-t%E1%BB%AD-ca/poem-RlHU8XG2KzX_YJ1aClmr-A">Từ khanh nhị tử ca - 徐卿二子歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br></div>	</div>
